S100XC:S100_ExchangeCatalogue.S100XC:exchangeCatalogueDescription: This exchange catalogue contains forecast guidance of surface water currents that have been generated from NOAA operational oceanographic forecast systems. The information has been repackaged into IHO S-111 compliant data sets for distribution to navigation systems.
S100XC:S100_ExchangeCatalogue.S100XC:exchangeCatalogueComment: This Exchange Set Catalogue was created for testing purposes
